import '../styles/Login.scss'


import Link from 'next/link'



const Login = () => (
  <section className="login">
	<form>
		  <label>
		    email:
		    <input type="text" name="name" />
		  </label>
		  
		  <label>
		    password:
		    <input type="text" name="name" />
		  </label>
		  
		  <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
	</form>
  </section>
)

export default Login
